snippet.title: Voodoo Vince: Remastered Trailer
snippet.description: Voodoo Vince returns after hiding for 13 years in the back of the Voodoo shop. Get ready to run and jump your way through a series of devilish, twisted challenges as Vince fights to save his creator, Madam Charmaine. Coming April 18, 2017 for Xbox One, Windows 10 and Steam.
